    {
      "content" : [
        {
          "anchor" : "overview",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Overview",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The basic L-system is a ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/Lindenmayer\/documentation\/Lindenmayer\/ContextualLSystem",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : ", which you create with a starting point made up of one or more instances of a type that conforms to ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/Lindenmayer\/documentation\/Lindenmayer\/Module",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The type ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/Lindenmayer\/documentation\/Lindenmayer\/RandomContextualLSystem",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " includes a seed-able random number generator, to support including randomness in the rule rewriting.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "The and seed-able nature of the random number generator allows the L-system to be explicitly deterministic.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "To create an L-system that includes a random number generator, call ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "create(_:with:)",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " with an instance of a seed-able random number generator.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "If you pass ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "nil",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : ", the L-system will be created with a pseudo-random number generator using the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/github.com\/heckj\/Squirrel3",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " swift package.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The type ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/Lindenmayer\/documentation\/Lindenmayer\/ParameterizedRandomContextualLSystem",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " includes a seed-able random number generator as well as a type that you provide that gets provided to the closures you write when defining rules.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "This type can contain any number of parameters that you can use when within the closures for your rules, and makes a convenient container for common values used in multiple rules.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind" : "content"
    }
  ],
